Redesign objectives
===================

1. provide a bare-bones improved content hierarchy.
2. focus on usability.
3. do not solve aesthetic issues.  make note of them if necessary.
4. remove unnecessary markup.
5. don't optimise css.
6. if unnecessary markup can't be removed without optimising css, leave it there and make note.

Redesigns
=========

Navigation - index.html
- begin from webmocks/2013/content_design and docs/2013/contentmap_proposed2.md.
- final output in layout.haml

Scoreboard - user.html, scoreboard.html


